- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning algorithms for finite automata.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a learning algorithm.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning and automata theory, which are both relevant to AI.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as automata theory has applications in cryptography and security.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with algorithms for learning automata.
